OL,3,CM621 closed after woman hit by car
OL,5,FThe M621 in Leeds was closed on Friday
OL,6,Fmorning after a woman was hit by a car.
OL,8,FDrivers were warned the closure would
OL,9,Fbe in place "for some time" following
OL,10,Fthe incident on the clockwise side of
OL,11,Fthe motorway, West Yorkshire Police
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FOfficers were called at 4.50am
OL,15,Ffollowing reports of a collision with
OL,16,Fa woman who was "in the carriageway"
OL,17,Fnear junction one for Holbeck at the
OL,18,Ftime.
OL,20,FShe suffered serious injuries.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
