OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1776096667
OL,3,CM621 closed after woman hit by car
OL,5,FA police spokesperson said: "The
OL,6,Fincident remains ongoing and a full
OL,7,Froad closure remains in place on both
OL,8,Fsides of the carriageway with
OL,9,Fdiversions in place.
OL,11,F"The closure is expected to be in
OL,12,Fplace for some time and motorists are
OL,13,Fthanked for their patience while
OL,14,Fnecessary incident investigation work
OL,15,Ftakes place."
